reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2022
reviews.reviewText: Looks like this is our “new normal,” so stock up on these! They have a soft silk feel, comfortable to wear, everything they claim to be! They are lightweight, so breathing is comfy; they fit snugly with no chin, nose or side gapping. I can wear these for a long period of time & feel protected. The 5 pack at the price is great, gives you 1 for every work day. They can be washed by machine or hand, I hung to dry, (in lieu of dryer), they dry fast. Would like to see more solid colors & prints! Stay safe & get these!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 5, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for price!!!!!
reviews.reviewText: I was really nervous about buying masks online but I am super happy about them. The adjustable straps helps the mask fit to my face better (as I have a smaller face) and the material is light and breathable. Unlike some masks that stick to your nose while you breath in. It also has a great contour to my nose and chin. It does not flow down to my neck or rub against my neck which I really like. Shipping took a bit longer than prime two-day shipping but that was not an issue for me. Overall, super light-weight, comfortable and breathable!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 14, 2021
reviews.reviewText: 100% our favorite masks. Hold up great with multiple washings. Fit our fat faces comfortably. We call them 'the good masks'. Where are the good masks? Are the good masks all dirty? You get the picture. Great quality, not hard to breath in, not too thick, we live in the desert so that's important. Doesn't stick to you if you get sweaty.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 24, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Good look and comfort. Fails water test
reviews.reviewText: This works well if you wear a mask simply because it's a mandate. If you're the type of person who wants to wear 1 effective mask, this isn't for you. This failed the water test miserably. Water soaked in like it's cotton. No beading what so ever, so I can't trust this will protect me from a cough. But this mask is really thick and quite comfortable so it deserves credit for that. It's a great looking mask for it you want to wear it over your n95 our medical mask too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 18, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great mask for the price!
reviews.reviewText: I’m a teacher and have to wear a mask all day every day. My problem is that the cotton fabric ones you buy at the store or have made, get extremely itchy and irritable by the end of the day. These were not perfect at the beginning because I felt like there was a bit more fabric than I was used to, however not I just get mad when I can’t find them or they’re dirty, because they ARE my favorite.The only slight negative is that while the straps are adjustable, the ear pieces are still pretty short. I may have 1/4” left before the little doodad falls off the ends. So if you have a big face, get a bigger size!
